slovenian.helpPanelText = "This simulator demonstrates the correspondence between the moon's position in its orbit, its phase, and its position in an observer's sky at different times of day.";
slovenian.helpPanelText += "<br><br>The upper left panel shows the orbit visualization. The moon can be dragged around to change its position, and the earth can be dragged around to change its rotation. You can also use the <b>Animation and Time Controls</b> panel to control the simulation.";
